===Expression===
'''[[話す|話せば]][[分かる|わかる]]

#The proverbial phrase which is appealing: "You'll be convinced if you listen to me."
#:''話せばわかる。じっくり話し合おうよ。''
#:''はなせばわかる。じっくりはなしあおうよ。''
#:''You'll be convinced if you just listen to me. Why don't you sit down and talk with me?''

